---
title: Seth’s Asian Pork Dumplings with Quick-Pickled Veggie Salad and Soy Dipping Sauce
description: Who knew it was so easy to make this take-out classic at home? With the help of versatile wonton wrappers, these juicy dumplings are a breeze. Served with a crunchy salad for contrast, this take-out makeover won’t weigh you down.
